If anyone feels compelled to partecipate in this project, either for intellectual pleasure or for real interest, 
this is a list of profiles probably needed to develop this framework and that will be gladly welcomed to contribute.
Don't feel shy to inquire, it's not like is a paid job...

Profile 1 — Mechanism Design Theorist
       (Mathematics of Koinism's constitutional architecture)
Profile 2 — Political Economist on Fiscal Institutions
       (Flat tax and resource consumption tax in a realistic scenario)
Profile 3 — Labour Economist
       (UBIES floor against working rights to solve destitution and rethink the Employer/worker relationship)
Profile 4 — Computational Economist
       (To build the formal model of the fiscal arithmetic)
Profile 5 — Institutional / Constitutional Political Economist
       (To contribute in institution design)
Profile 6 — Fiscal Federalism Specialist
       (Koinism in a federal europe)
Profile 7 — Evolutionary Economist
       (To show that the framework's assumptions about human behaviour are grounded 
        in evolutionary science rather than wishful thinking)
Profile 8 — Demographer
       (To show how Koinism could affect the fertility crisis)
Profile 9 — One Health Researcher
       (To study the concept of theft and exchange between human and non-human Koines)
Profile 10 — Evolutionary Anthropologist
       (To show how the empirical claims are grounded in the cross-cultural research that 
        shows which features of human behaviour are universal and which are culturally specific)
Profile 11 — Social Epidemiologist
       (To show how financial precarity is a measurable damage both to the individuals and the system)
Profile 12 — Community Psychologist
       (To show the damage of means-testing welfare and the benefits of proactive social work)
Profile 13 — Behavioural Economist
       (To study the possible behaviour of people in a Koinist society)
Profile 14 — Constitutional Lawyer
       (The grounding of the previous constitutional design)
Profile 15 — Institutional Historian
       (Provide the historical record that proves kleptocracy borns through the accumulation of privilege)
Profile 16 — Science Communicator
       (To provide the best vocabulary to make this work understandable without losing meaning)

However this wants to be an open work and any contribution is likely appreciated.

